If you don't go to college, exactly when do you expect to do all of this?</font></span><p><font size=1><font color=#f6f6ef>-----</font></font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table border=0><tr><td><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/s.gif" height=1 width=40></td><td valign=top><center><a id=up_1866446 href="vote?for=1866446&dir=up&whence=%2f%78%3f%66%6e%69%64%3d%7a%32%4a%56%6c%78%74%51%35%38"><img src="http://ycombinator.com/images/grayarrow.gif" border=0 vspace=3 hspace=2></a><span id=down_1866446></span></center></td><td class="default"><div style="margin-top:2px; margin-bottom:-10px; "><span class="comhead"><a href="user?id=Deejahll">Deejahll</a> 458 days ago  | <a href="item?id=1866446">link</a></span></div><br>
